<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>11163</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>18593</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我希望我们很快就能到达西方极乐世界。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>18594</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>26710</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一天早上唐僧说。悟空他们这时正在吃早饭。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>26711</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>32463</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空大笑。“这一趟要走很多年的，师父！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>32464</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>36506</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一路上你必须经历很多磨难。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>36507</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>39737</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>佛祖不会随便把真经给人的。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>39738</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>46521</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>你必须经历漫长而艰难的旅程，才能证明你值得得到真经。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>46522</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>52258</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>唐僧叹了口气。八戒放下了碗。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>52259</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>55952</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我不想走了！”他大叫，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>55953</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>60559</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我的腿疼死了。我们没有一次吃饱过。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>60560</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>64632</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“别再想着吃的了，八戒。”悟空说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>64633</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>66719</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们现在是僧人了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>66720</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>71530</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我们应该一心想着去西天极乐世界。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>71531</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>80095</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>八戒叹了口气。他洗好碗后，三个人又上路了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>80096</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>83791</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>很快他们就到了一条河边。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>83792</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>91626</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>河里水花飞溅，一个紫色的妖怪从河中跳了出来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>91627</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>95034</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“师父，退后！”悟空大叫。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>95035</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>101380</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他拿出了金箍棒挡住了妖怪的杖。咣当！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>101381</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>106567</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>八戒朝着妖怪冲去，挥舞着他的钉耙。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>106568</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>109647</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>妖怪又跳回了河里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>109648</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>113192</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“八戒，我水性不好。”悟空说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>113193</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>118695</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你到水里，引他上来，然后我给他一个突然袭击。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>118696</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>123787</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“好。”八戒说，“等他上岸，我就堵住他的退路，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>123788</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>127575</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>这样他就没办法再回到河里了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>127576</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>132967</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>八戒跳进了水里。悟空在河边等着。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>132968</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>138455</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>过了一会儿，八戒出来了，身后跟着那妖怪。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>138456</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>143455</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空挥舞着金箍棒打过去，但没打中。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>143456</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>148058</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>那妖怪又跳回了水里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>148059</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>153763</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你都没等到他上岸。”八戒说，“你太没耐心了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>153764</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>157775</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空耸耸肩笑了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>157776</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>161890</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们对着妖怪叫骂吧。也许他会出来的。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>161891</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>166710</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空和八戒对着河面叫骂了一个多小时，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>166711</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>171048</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但那妖怪始终没有再出来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>171049</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>177297</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>最后悟空叹了口气：“有那妖怪在河里，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>177298</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>182006</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我们就没办法过去。我去请观音菩萨帮忙。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>182007</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>189027</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空到了普陀山，将妖怪的事情告诉了观音菩萨。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>189028</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>194739</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“他名叫沙悟净。”观音菩萨说，“他在等你们。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>194740</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>199635</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他会护送唐僧到达西方极乐世界。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>199636</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>203015</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我不知道啊！”悟空大叫。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>203016</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>208762</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>观音菩萨和悟空一起回到了河边。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>208763</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>214919</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“沙悟净！”她叫道，“唐僧来了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>214920</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>219902</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>那妖怪从河里跳了出来拜倒在地。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>219903</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>225393</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“抱歉，观音菩萨。”他说，“我不知道唐僧来了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>225394</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>230063</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这两个是他的徒弟。”观音菩萨说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>230064</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>234190</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她用手指了指悟空和八戒。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>234191</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>239311</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟净看上去很吃惊：“他们打了我！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>239312</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>242850</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你先打我们的！”八戒高叫。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>242851</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>250809</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“别吵了。”观音菩萨说，“悟净，你要帮着唐僧去西天。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>250810</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>254305</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是，观音菩萨。”悟净说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>254306</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>259704</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>观音菩萨消失了，悟净加入了队伍。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>259705</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>264580</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>唐僧骑马的时候他就牵着马。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>264581</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>270370</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我因为打碎了天庭的琉璃而受惩罚。”一天悟净说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>270371</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>274707</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“等我们到了西方极乐世界，我就可以被宽恕。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>274708</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>281139</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“八戒和我也是因为在天庭犯了事而被罚的。”悟空说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>281140</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>286095</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这马也是。你知道吗？这马其实是一条龙。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>55</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>286096</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>292843</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟净看上去很怀疑：“这马的速度太慢了，不可能是龙啊。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>56</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>292844</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>297882</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哦，真的吗？”悟空说，“你看！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>57</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>297883</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>304192</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他拍了一下马。那马像闪电一样在路上飞跑。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>58</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>304193</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>308553</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>它的缰绳从悟净的手里滑脱了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>59</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>308554</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>311504</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“啊！”唐僧大叫。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>60</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>311505</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>320658</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>当马最终停下来的时候，唐僧已经在一座黑暗森林里了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>61</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>320659</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>324024</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他害怕地一直大喘气。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>62</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>324025</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>330104</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>那森林里有很多狼、熊，还有老虎！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>